CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

August 29, 2008

[Cite as 08/29/2008 Case Announcements, 2008-Ohio-4377.]

MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

2008-1196. Deitrick v. Mentor.

Lake App. No. 2007-L-084, 2008-0hio-2138. This cause is pending before the court as a discretionary appeal. Upon consideration of appellant’s application for dismissal,

It is ordered by the court that the application for dismissal is granted. Accordingly, this cause is dismissed.
